name: sfchronicle
text:
Starting today, customers can line up at Tato on Fridays for a taco plate and pay between zero and $10. 

Each time someone pays the full $10 price, Tato will donate a meal to people residing in COVID hotels or homeless shelters. https://t.co/Xi4iJSfpIi
